    "title": "The Architecture of Scale: How I Made My MCP Tools Agent-Writable",
    "description": "When Google released Nano Banana 2, my image tools became obsolete overnight. Here's how I rebuilt my MCP tool builder so agents could compose, test, and deploy tools without touching framework code.",
