    "content": "AI has changed everything.\n\nOld VHS recordings. Faded paper photos. Grainy phone snapshots. Until recently, these were just... gone. The detail wasn't there to recover.\n\nNow it is. Pixel uses Google's latest Gemini model to restore images to **hyper-realistic 4K**. Not upscaled. Restored.\n\nYou can see yourself young again. Clearer than you remember.\n\n---\n\n## My Memories, Restored\n\n### Hungary, 1991\n\nMe in kindergarten. Originally a VHS recording. Now restored to 4K.\n\n<SplitPreview\n  originalUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_49d6efb916aec77949d6efb916aec779/originals/0532f497-5f7d-4b47-8361-ea6e83df817b.png\"\n  enhancedUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_49d6efb916aec77949d6efb916aec779/enhanced/0532f497-5f7d-4b47-8361-ea6e83df817b/cmj75u2yy000104l2fmdwa5ax.jpg\"\n  originalLabel=\"VHS Original\"\n  enhancedLabel=\"4K Restored\"\n/>\n\n### Brighton Pier\n\nI took a photo of an old photo. The result looks like it came from a DSLR.\n\n<SplitPreview\n  originalUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_b492619127d7e0c1c8338d243d71a977/originals/5b384972-3086-418e-946a-f9c57e2765c4.jpeg\"\n  enhancedUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_b492619127d7e0c1c8338d243d71a977/enhanced/5b384972-3086-418e-946a-f9c57e2765c4.jpeg\"\n  originalLabel=\"Phone Snap\"\n  enhancedLabel=\"DSLR Quality\"\n/>\n\n### A Friend\n\nShe's over 30 today. This photo is from another era. She cried when she saw it restored.\n\n<SplitPreview\n  originalUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_b492619127d7e0c1c8338d243d71a977/originals/fcfc6f3c-7b60-4b05-a636-0ec786b13521.jpeg\"\n  enhancedUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_b492619127d7e0c1c8338d243d71a977/enhanced/fcfc6f3c-7b60-4b05-a636-0ec786b13521.jpeg\"\n  originalLabel=\"Original\"\n  enhancedLabel=\"Enhanced\"\n/>\n\n### Family, 1986\n\nMum, Dad, my brother, and me. Taken from a paper photo.\n\n<ImageComparisonSlider\n  originalUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_49d6efb916aec77949d6efb916aec779/originals/80eeae12-bedb-4b4e-90bc-60e1a07a323c.png\"\n  enhancedUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_49d6efb916aec77949d6efb916aec779/enhanced/80eeae12-bedb-4b4e-90bc-60e1a07a323c/cmj5mr8i2000h04l8vfm1giv7.jpg\"\n  originalLabel=\"Paper Photo\"\n  enhancedLabel=\"Restored\"\n/>\n\n### Brighton, 2025\n\nMy dog. His name is Pixel. Photo taken with a Google Pixel phone. Enhanced by my app, also called Pixel. Built with Google's Gemini.\n\nAm I a Google fanboy? **Pixel.**\n\n<SplitPreview\n  originalUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_49d6efb916aec77949d6efb916aec779/originals/c5e90fec-cc8a-4785-9e19-4b95b00903df.jpeg\"\n  enhancedUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_49d6efb916aec77949d6efb916aec779/enhanced/c5e90fec-cc8a-4785-9e19-4b95b00903df/cmj5wk97w000304l70noq4tn1.jpg\"\n  originalLabel=\"Google Pixel\"\n  enhancedLabel=\"App Pixel\"\n/>\n\n### Me, 2015\n\nSuch a handsome guy. Now in 4K.\n\n<SplitPreview\n  originalUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_49d6efb916aec77949d6efb916aec779/originals/5ff8ba3c-7b23-4a1e-b9fd-14a7c3da15ab.jpeg\"\n  enhancedUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_49d6efb916aec77949d6efb916aec779/enhanced/5ff8ba3c-7b23-4a1e-b9fd-14a7c3da15ab/cmj5mq0xv000304le96338hpb.jpg\"\n  originalLabel=\"Original\"\n  enhancedLabel=\"4K\"\n/>\n\n### Me, 2015\n\nSame night. Different angle. Same 4K treatment.\n\n<SplitPreview\n  originalUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_b492619127d7e0c1c8338d243d71a977/originals/4b15d13f-d2b1-4ba5-896f-1deef9d039af.jpeg\"\n  enhancedUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_b492619127d7e0c1c8338d243d71a977/enhanced/4b15d13f-d2b1-4ba5-896f-1deef9d039af.jpeg\"\n  originalLabel=\"Original\"\n  enhancedLabel=\"4K\"\n/>\n\n### Hungary, 1982\n\nMy grandparents. Still alive in this photo.\n\n<SplitPreview\n  originalUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_49d6efb916aec77949d6efb916aec779/originals/50c0e4c6-d2d2-4d9d-8a89-d4e031d459c5.jpeg\"\n  enhancedUrl=\"https://pub-cf0adddb5752426a96ef090997e0da95.r2.dev/users/user_49d6efb916aec77949d6efb916aec779/enhanced/50c0e4c6-d2d2-4d9d-8a89-d4e031d459c5/cmj61bfze000104l8k1nphicr.jpg\"\n  originalLabel=\"1982\"\n  enhancedLabel=\"Restored\"\n/>\n\n---\n\n## Try It Yourself\n\nUpload any photo. Old or new. One click. 4K.\n\n**[Try Pixel Free](/apps/pixel)** — First enhancement is on us.\n\n---\n\nYour memories deserve to be seen clearly.\n\n*— Zoltan (and Pixel the dog, supervising from Brighton)*"
